  <description type="morphology">Stems mostly spreading, 0.5–2 dm, glabrous. Leaves basal and cauline; basal petiolate, petiole 0.5–2 cm, blade spatulate, (1–)2–4 × (0.5–)1–2.5 cm, glabrous; cauline sessile, blade narrowly lanceolate to oblanceolate, 0.5–4.5 × 0.2–1 cm. Inflorescences spreading, 0.5–2.5(–3) dm, glabrous, occasionally glandular at proximal nodes; bracts 0.5–4 mm. Peduncles straight, slender to filiform, 0.1–4 cm, glabrous, or absent. Involucral bracts 2–8 × 2–3 mm, glabrous. Flowers: perianth yellow, 1.5–3 mm; tepals lanceolate; filaments 1.5–2 mm; anthers 0.2–0.3 mm. Achenes 2–2.5 mm. 2n = 40.</description>
